---+ !! UKP Mail Service

---++ Microsoft Outlook 2007

*Note:* this is the only officially supported client

Microsoft Outlook 2007 is available in the Windows VM on your workstation. When you start it, enter your details into the dialogs presented to you and leave it to Outlook to detect all settings automatically. If any problem occurs, please contact system-admin by opening an issue the issue tracker.

---++ Thunderbird

